en.name: M16A2 5.56x45 upper receiver
en.description: An upper receiver for the M16A2 assault rifle manufactured by Colt.

en.name: NL545 (DI) 5.45x39 upper receiver
en.description: An upper receiver for the direct impingement NL545 assault rifle manufactured by Custom Guns. Equipped with a mount for attaching additional devices.

en.name: NL545 (GP) 5.45x39 upper receiver (FDE)
en.description: An upper receiver for the short-stroke gas piston NL545 assault rifle manufactured by Custom Guns. Equipped with a mount for attaching additional devices. Flat Dark Earth version.

en.name: M16A1E1 5.56x45 upper receiver
en.description: An upper receiver for the M16A1E1 assault rifle manufactured by Colt. An early prototype variant between the M16A1 and M16A2, which also served as the basis for the Canadian C7. During the 1980s it was widely fitted to various special carbines produced by Colt.

en.name: AR-15 Radian Weapons Model 1 5.56x45 upper receiver
en.description: A precision CNC machined upper receiver for the AR-15 platform. Manufactured by Radian Weapons.

en.name: AK-308 railed dust cover
en.description: A standard receiver dust cover with an integrated Picatinny rail for AK-308 assault rifles. Manufactured by Kalashnikov Group.

en.name: TKPD railed dust cover
en.description: A receiver top cover for the TKPD assault carbine. Equipped with a Picatinny rail for installation of optics.
